editing tools. The current work highlights results from a qualitative user study of
real-world Japanese and U.S. distributed work teams who used LiveDeck, a real-time
slide editing and whiteboarding tool. Through the implementation of various novel
features used as probes, differences in behavior and attitudes between team members
were uncovered. Differences in the use of slide navigation options, anonymity features,
