A case study of an older person's experience shows the techniques supporting her to
reconceive her response to technology. In particular, we analyze how using a "prop"
as a design artifact allows her to imagine new possibilities and take a more assertive
role.},
booktitle = {Proceedings of the SIGCHI Conference on Human Factors in Computing Systems},
