important. We present ClearPlate - a new optical unit for image capture. It has a
physically transparent viewfinder through which the user can observe the target directly
without offset; the framed image is captured by the built-in camera. We also present
a user study that evaluates ClearPlate performance in the 2D barcode acquisition task.
